snippet.title: Amber Heard secretly welcomes baby girl Oonagh via surrogate.
snippet.description:
The 21st BET Awards will take place on June 27, 2021. The ceremony celebrates achievements in entertainment and honors music, sports, television, and movies.

The nominees were announced on May 27, 2021. DaBaby and Megan Thee Stallion received the most nominations with 7 each, ahead of Cardi B and Drake, who tied with five nominations each.[1][2][3]

On June 14, it was announced that actress Taraji P. Henson will host the ceremony for the first time, and that musician and actress Queen Latifah will be honored with the Lifetime Achievement AwardSource: newspaper,various article,instagram account,wikipedia,pinkvilla
